# Planner Portfolio - beyond-de-giorgi / run-002

## Preserved Context

- `beta = 4/3` is already sharp for the De Giorgi-Vasseur route. This portfolio does not spend budget on more De Giorgi tuning, stronger-type pressure bounds, or relabeled `H^1/BMO` variants.
